===Most frequent venues===
With seventeen telecasts hosted, the [[Staples Center]] have hosted the most Grammy telecasts. The Staples Center surpassed the Shrine Auditorium as the most frequent host in 2017. The Shrine Auditorium hosted sixteen times between 1978 and 1999.
